properties.Name: ContractTermType
properties.Description:
A Contract Term that may be applied to a Contract.

Ex:
- No signed contract required
- Volume order incentive
- Next Day Delivery
- 7 Day Delivery
- Number Of Delivery Days
- Reference Currency
- Same day settlement
- Next day settlement
- Third day settlement

Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Contract Term Type.

Columns.Description: The name of a Contract Term Type.

Columns.Name: ContractTermTypeDescription
Columns.Description: The description of a Contract Term Type.
